### What is Hive?
#### Hive is an ETL(Extract, Transform, Load) & data warehouse tool built on HDFS. Hive is to make you job easy.

### Why Hive?
1. ETL process using Map-Reduce needs a lot of code, which is diffcult to write. Hive provides you a SQL-like interface over HDFS. 
It helps you to write SQL-Like queries, which internally gets converted to Map-Reduce job.
2. Easy to write
3. Good for warehouse purpose
4. Supports partitions & bucket

For detailed information: https://www.guru99.com/introduction-hive.html
